question: List all of the titles and the amount of funding that has been dispersed per programme
text: List all of the titles and the amount of funding that has been dispersed per programme
sql: SELECT programmes.title, sum(projects.ec_max_contribution) FROM programmes  JOIN project_programmes  ON programmes.code = project_programmes.programme JOIN projects  ON projects.unics_id = project_programmes.project GROUP BY programmes.title
